track.name: The Rooster
comments: 10 years later still think Speakerboxxx is the better side.
best track on speakerboxx/the love below. AND Big Boi is better than Dre, come on, start a argument you pussies!
This track reminds me of why I'm just about strictly old skool when it comes to rap.
"You fuss, fight, fart" my favorite part. This track is genius!
Big Boi really knows how to catch your attention. Rather you like it or not, you will watch him completely.

You gotta have love and respect for OutKast's don't-give-a-damn, be-as-different-as-we-wanna-be-attitude. It's what puts them in a different stratosphere from everybody else. The movie soundtrack version of this is a mighty fine track too.
